---
title: Sweet Chili Pork Bowls with Bell Pepper & Peanuts
description: Forget takeout: the path to sweet-and-savory dinner bliss is only 30 minutes away! In this recipe, pork, pepper, and onion are coated in a sumptuous sweet chili sauce, and peanuts are transformed into the perfect crunchy topping. Everything comes together over a bed of fluffy rice. The results? A symphony of flavors and textures so delicious, you might just lick the plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5efb358e43975d50ea6927d2-03092082.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-chili-pork-bowls-5efb358e43975d50ea6927d2-9d12e1ff.pdf
course: main course
cuisine: Asian
